2005-03-20 ekohl

   tools/widl/client.c
   tools/widl/server.c

Improve error messages.
Don't start counting the type_offset for each new fuction. It is a global offset.
Use only basic types in type- and proc-strings (e.g. unsigned long -> long).


2005-03-13 ekohl

   tools/widl/server.c

Remove debug printf().


